Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.75,0:02:16.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fad(200,100)}{\fs45\shad3\4a&H00&}第三话 危机中的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.75,0:02:21.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,比赛一开始 发展就出乎意料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.25,0:02:23.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第一站 美国杯车赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.15,0:02:25.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,领先带头的是这次大赛中出道的菲尔·弗利兹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.25,0:02:30.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他在预赛首日就以惊人圈速取得领先位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.45,0:02:32.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而在这场决赛中也成了他独领风骚的局面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.15,0:02:35.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就连第二位的队友加贺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.15,0:02:38.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也已经被抛离到40秒以上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.15,0:02:42.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可恶!这样一开始就变得不是在赛车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.75,0:02:45.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,又来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.05,0:02:49.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你在干什么!慢了一整圈的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.35,0:02:54.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,开什么玩笑 我不是为了让人超车而比赛的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.35,0:02:57.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你别太过分了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.95,0:03:08.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,相撞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.25,0:03:10.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,风见隼人和...这位...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.75,0:03:12.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,车号7号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.15,0:03:14.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,失落之环的雷欧·安哈特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.65,0:03:16.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,风见果然很急
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.15,0:03:18.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在这里和慢一圈的车子相撞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.85,0:03:20.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不得已退出了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.65,0:03:22.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,倒霉透顶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.35,0:03:24.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是我第一场比赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.95,0:03:33.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好了 迎接的准备做好了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.35,0:03:38.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,颁奖典礼和后来的采访是逃避不了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.25,0:03:41.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,菲尔得做好这个工作才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.25,0:03:44.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,AL-ZARD现在接受挥舞的方格子旗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.35,0:03:47.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,多么从容的胜利啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.85,0:03:48.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,菲尔·弗利兹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.15,0:03:50.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一出道就拿下第一优先位置和胜利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.35,0:03:53.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,继兰德尔之后史上第二个创下此快举的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.15,0:03:59.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你到底打算怎样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.85,0:04:02.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们争夺前头的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.85,0:04:04.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只有互相信任对方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.15,0:04:05.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,才可能做到极限边缘的竞争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.45,0:04:09.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而你这今天才出道一下子就想模仿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.45,0:04:10.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,当然不可能成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.55,0:04:14.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那样跑法有危险的不只你自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.15,0:04:16.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,周围的人也可能遭到波及
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.95,0:04:18.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这点道理你该知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.75,0:04:21.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抱歉 抱歉 风见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.95,0:04:23.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今天的事我代他向你道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.25,0:04:26.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你向我道歉是没用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.05,0:04:28.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我想说的是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.45,0:04:33.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我非常了解 可是也别太过火了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.95,0:04:36.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,被媒体知道了就麻烦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.75,0:04:38.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.45,0:04:42.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我会好好教训他的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.85,0:04:44.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,最好这么做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.25,0:04:47.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果你还想让他在下一场车赛跑的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.05,0:04:52.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.25,0:04:57.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有什么了不起的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.85,0:05:01.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别开玩笑了 小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.05,0:05:01.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂 走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.65,0:05:04.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好痛...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.45,0:05:08.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,气死人了!那算什么态度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.15,0:05:10.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过是个新人罢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.45,0:05:13.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,扔得好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.75,0:05:15.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,气死我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.65,0:05:18.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.35,0:05:23.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎呀 有点受宠若惊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.05,0:05:25.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,觉得好像成了电影明星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.85,0:05:27.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那当然呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.55,0:05:30.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为你们之前从来没透露任何消息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.55,0:05:33.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们可是连弗利兹的声音也没听过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.55,0:05:37.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这真是对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.65,0:05:40.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是比赛前惊动大家没什么意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.35,0:05:44.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,新人在出道前都是很紧张的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.15,0:05:46.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再施加多余的压力上去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.25,0:05:48.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,往往就无法发挥出实力了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.85,0:05:52.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那就是说 你们一开始就知道他会优胜吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.25,0:05:54.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可以这么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.65,0:05:58.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这也是我们和AL-ZARD存在的目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.05,0:06:02.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那么说 名云社长你一开始就看好弗利兹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.15,0:06:04.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而不是加贺吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.05,0:06:07.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,实际上现在加贺只跑到第五名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.95,0:06:10.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果没那个打转的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.05,0:06:11.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他或许会得第二名吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.65,0:06:15.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,即使那样 他和菲尔还是差很远
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.35,0:06:19.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他们俩的车子在外观上有些不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.65,0:06:21.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不同的只是外观吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.35,0:06:25.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,它的智能系统也有些不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.75,0:06:28.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,AL-ZARD是以有机物质为介质
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.85,0:06:31.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,采用了生化计算机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.95,0:06:35.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不熟悉的人很难驾驶它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.95,0:06:41.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以加贺的车子里采用的是旧有的开发系统
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.35,0:06:43.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,其余的都一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.45,0:06:46.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,包括稀有金属变型系统也一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.45,0:06:52.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是我期待菲尔的理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.55,0:06:55.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他本来就是这部车的测试员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.95,0:06:57.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以非常熟练
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.35,0:06:59.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如此而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.55,0:07:03.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,绝不是我认为加贺能力不足
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.55,0:07:08.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,弗利兹先生\N请问你驾驶高智能方程式有何感受？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.25,0:07:14.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,菲尔 喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.35,0:07:17.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不会是要在这地方睡着吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.15,0:07:22.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我知道你很累
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.35,0:07:24.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但那位女性有问题问你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.35,0:07:27.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,问你参加高智能方程式有何感受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.05,0:07:38.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,能和风见先生...古德利安先生...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.65,0:07:43.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在同一赛车场上比赛...我很高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.35,0:07:47.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为那是我的梦想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.95,0:07:52.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果下次能和他们两人较量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.75,0:07:55.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.65,0:07:56.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,菲尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.15,0:08:00.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那也要等他们两人追上你的车才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.95,0:08:05.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的难以置信呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.75,0:08:08.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他在那斯卡车赛一直是垫底的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.45,0:08:11.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这表示他很努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.05,0:08:13.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,和你不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.55,0:08:16.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这么讲太过分了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.25,0:08:19.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好疼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.95,0:08:26.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可恶 是谁在这地方乱扔香蕉皮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.25,0:08:36.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你认为谁拥有足够跟风见和古德利安竞赛的技术？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.95,0:08:39.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别搞错了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.05,0:08:43.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你只是为了在前头接受方格旗挥舞而存在的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.95,0:08:51.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没关系 没关系啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.95,0:08:56.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,退出我才不在乎呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.25,0:08:57.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,走着瞧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.15,0:09:02.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,下一场我就是优胜者!冠军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.75,0:09:05.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真不像样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.15,0:09:07.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那也算高智能方程式的车手吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.15,0:09:10.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你听过「猴子的屁股笑话」吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.85,0:09:11.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,屁股笑话?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.25,0:09:13.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是日本的谚语
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.45,0:09:16.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然自己的屁股也是红色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.35,0:09:19.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,却笑其它的猴子的红屁股
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.15,0:09:22.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我认为那和现在的你很贴切呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.75,0:09:27.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 对方看来更年轻更受欢迎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.05,0:09:28.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.65,0:09:29.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,结账
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.85,0:09:34.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你这么晚去哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.55,0:09:36.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我要先一步回德国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.85,0:09:40.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别因为我不在就做出脱轨行为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.55,0:09:43.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在就走?那边已经是深夜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.55,0:09:46.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,难道你想在下一站也有同样的遭遇吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.35,0:09:50.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们要尽快采取应变措施
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.95,0:09:53.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不然以后哪一个车队都会难以应付
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.85,0:09:55.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.25,0:09:58.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,幸好你看来被甩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.35,0:10:00.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快点回房睡觉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.05,0:10:02.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是最好的方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.85,0:10:03.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.85,0:10:07.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,双重打击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.75,0:10:12.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还是别去了 风见先生已经很累了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.65,0:10:15.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他比赛被迫退出 心情好像非常不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.85,0:10:17.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,会挨骂的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.85,0:10:20.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以我们才要更努力安慰他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.85,0:10:23.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一直呆在房里太无聊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.25,0:10:28.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,前辈他不在房里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.15,0:10:34.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,吓死我了 安尼先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.65,0:10:38.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请问...风见先生去哪里了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.65,0:10:41.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不知道 总之他不在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.65,0:10:43.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们有什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.75,0:10:46.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不...没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.95,0:10:48.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,打扰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.55,0:10:49.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.65,0:10:52.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对不起...等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.15,0:10:56.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,前辈哪有时间理你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.65,0:11:05.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,难得我做了个防止退场的护身符
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.15,0:11:09.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以 希尔结果通宵完成报告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.75,0:11:12.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,隔天就第一个拿着报告去道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.25,0:11:14.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然他终于被原谅了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.45,0:11:17.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但大家说那个教授不会就那样算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.75,0:11:21.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,下次轮到他那就糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.25,0:11:27.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.75,0:11:30.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一直想着已经结束了的车赛没有用的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.75,0:11:31.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,结束？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.15,0:11:35.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,开什么玩笑 车赛才刚刚开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.65,0:11:39.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是 你的焦躁是今天车赛引起的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.15,0:11:43.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我明白退场使你很不甘心 但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.05,0:11:49.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你什么都不知道就不要多嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.55,0:11:55.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.45,0:12:01.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想不到你们在这里约会呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.45,0:12:03.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们都变成大人了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.85,0:12:04.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,加贺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.05,0:12:07.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,晚上好 你一个人吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.65,0:12:10.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对 一个人 很可惜呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.45,0:12:13.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不介意的话 一起好吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.05,0:12:15.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.25,0:12:17.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不可以妨碍你们难得的约会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.95,0:12:19.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我请客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.55,0:12:28.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原来如此 脑中全是赛车的事吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.95,0:12:30.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还真像你的作风
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.25,0:12:34.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不可以吗?想着赛车的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.65,0:12:36.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 我没有说不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.45,0:12:44.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是 现在再怎么想也无济于事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.05,0:12:49.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是呢 赛车是快的人获胜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.25,0:12:52.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是理所当然的事阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.95,0:12:59.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我听说美琪和新条来了美国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.55,0:13:02.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊 算是修行之旅吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.25,0:13:06.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那家伙也真有趣 有那种想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.85,0:13:08.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,美琪好有勇气啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.55,0:13:10.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.95,0:13:13.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊 想想我还真是羡慕新条
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.65,0:13:16.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也想象他那样比赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.45,0:13:19.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,加贺你不是很幸运吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.05,0:13:21.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,能开那么快的赛车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.65,0:13:24.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然今天输了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.15,0:13:26.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但有了那种跑车要优胜也不是梦想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.55,0:13:29.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这么想开速度快的车子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.65,0:13:31.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你可以到葵车队来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.85,0:13:35.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果你肯替我付毁约的赔偿金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.05,0:13:36.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是随时都可以不干的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.05,0:13:38.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,加贺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.35,0:13:43.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我才不管那是不是什么最新科技
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.65,0:13:45.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但那种感觉恶劣的赛车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.35,0:13:48.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我以前从未开过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.35,0:13:51.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果你愿意替我开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.55,0:13:53.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我可是很高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.95,0:13:55.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,感觉恶劣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.45,0:14:03.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那车子设计时是完全不考虑车手的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.05,0:14:06.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只是追求快速 再快速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.25,0:14:08.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为此而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.15,0:14:10.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我渐渐不知道是我在驾驶它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.45,0:14:14.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还是它载着我来参加赛车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.65,0:14:21.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是 一直讲求速度下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.25,0:14:23.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,或许就会演变成那样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.25,0:14:25.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但我就是讨厌坐在那样的车上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.15,0:14:33.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对不起 话题变得浓重起来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.25,0:14:37.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是不是暂时无法和这家伙见面了呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.15,0:14:38.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不!不是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.25,0:14:40.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.05,0:14:43.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你别忘记
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.65,0:14:46.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们可不是在做车子性能的比赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.55,0:14:49.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是在赛车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.05,0:14:56.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.75,0:14:58.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是没有同等的力量的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.55,0:15:00.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,根本就不像是赛车啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.75,0:15:18.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那家伙又...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.75,0:15:33.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太了不起了 一开幕就两连胜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.45,0:15:36.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而且都是遥遥领先地冲线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.45,0:15:38.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不愧是名云
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.95,0:15:42.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要被速度快的车子载着跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.35,0:15:43.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,胜出是理所当然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.55,0:15:49.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不错 但是你以前没那样做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.05,0:15:52.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只有和多年奋斗的工作人员一起努力胜出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.35,0:15:53.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,才是真正的胜利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.15,0:15:57.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而这次竟然连车手在内撤换了一半工作人员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.35,0:16:01.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在的车队并非真正的葵车队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.35,0:16:03.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,无法达到目的的人被淘汰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.85,0:16:06.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是当然的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.45,0:16:09.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这我也知道 但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.35,0:16:15.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是将来要领导葵财团的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.15,0:16:16.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要有那种天真的想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.25,0:16:23.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,果然还是要给你找个理想的对象才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.95,0:16:25.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,父亲大人 那件事...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.15,0:16:30.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,例如 像名云那样的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.75,0:16:34.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我和会长都觉得他不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.25,0:16:39.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,若是名云 我应该可以把葵的将来交托给他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.35,0:16:41.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你说什么!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.35,0:16:45.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你也是时候要认真考虑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.05,0:16:48.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,幸好你跟名云的年纪相当
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.25,0:16:49.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别开玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.05,0:16:51.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谁会和那种人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.75,0:16:54.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,又来了 你总是那样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.35,0:16:58.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爸爸不会容许你任性了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.05,0:17:02.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为你选择丈夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.95,0:17:06.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也就是在选择葵将来的社长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.25,0:17:10.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{}第三站 加拿大杯 加斯帕湖赛车道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.85,0:17:28.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,连续三站都要退出 开什么玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.75,0:17:37.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是 力量汽缸改为 0.82吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.15,0:17:40.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,然后磁石离合器呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.85,0:17:42.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是 我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.45,0:17:46.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,换掉变档控制器和气压传动装置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.35,0:17:47.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.15,0:17:48.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.65,0:17:52.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,风见进入工作站已经超过30秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.85,0:17:54.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,情形看来很严重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.95,0:17:56.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他能回来赛车场吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.85,0:18:01.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.35,0:18:07.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.65,0:18:09.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不打电话询问的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.15,0:18:11.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们的工作人员就连维修都做不好吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.65,0:18:14.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,克蕾雅小姐也是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.55,0:18:16.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不知道她在日本做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.55,0:18:17.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但真混账
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.25,0:18:19.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,连赛车场都不来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.05,0:18:23.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 风见下车了 他退出了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.55,0:18:25.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,最近状态不好的风见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.45,0:18:28.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,继第一站后这站再度以退出结束比赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.25,0:18:33.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等等 隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.55,0:18:35.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刚才你说得太过分了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.75,0:18:38.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然不像克蕾雅小姐那么厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.75,0:18:39.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但良平也...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.85,0:18:41.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,比赛中结果就等于一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.25,0:18:44.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只有努力是不够的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.85,0:18:45.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.05,0:18:47.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,吵死人了 你到底想干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.85,0:18:52.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,反正现在返回赛道也无法胜出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.85,0:18:54.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,跑也是白跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.15,0:19:00.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,若是以前的隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.25,0:19:03.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他绝对不会说出那种话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.25,0:19:10.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不是说过无论何时机会是一定会有的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.35,0:19:13.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,少跟我说教了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.65,0:19:16.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有获胜的可能性还另当别论
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.45,0:19:20.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你以为拿一分两分会有什么用吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.75,0:19:24.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而且 说获胜不代表一切的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.85,0:19:25.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是明日香你吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.05,0:19:27.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还是说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.15,0:19:28.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,自己的男朋友没拿到优胜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.85,0:19:29.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你就不高兴?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.25,0:19:35.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,隼人...你那样说...太过分了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.05,0:19:40.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也没办法 这次…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.25,0:19:43.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不管我怎样努力都拿不到优胜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.55,0:19:48.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,放弃这场比赛在下次比赛拿分数比较…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.55,0:19:54.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,唷 你又说出没出息的话来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.25,0:19:57.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,兰德尔 你别偷听我们说话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.05,0:19:59.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是你先大吼大叫的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.65,0:20:05.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原来这就是最近你比赛自暴自弃的原因吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.05,0:20:07.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.55,0:20:08.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,明日香小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.25,0:20:11.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他的老毛病又犯了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.25,0:20:13.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把赢不了的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.95,0:20:15.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,推托在其他人身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.85,0:20:17.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,兰德尔!别说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.75,0:20:20.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那你说 你有办法赢吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.95,0:20:22.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,赢那辆车子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.35,0:20:26.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我再厉害也赢不了那家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.15,0:20:31.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是 我不是抱着你那种心情参加比赛的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.85,0:20:34.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这点在成绩上已经表现得很清楚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.65,0:20:41.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是 受不了你这种人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.75,0:20:46.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这就是11的冠军 打败我的男人的模样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.05,0:20:51.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.95,0:20:56.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,吵死了 不要连明日香你也令我心情烦躁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.85,0:21:00.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果你只懂说那些话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.95,0:21:02.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以后就别到赛车场来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.93,0:21:16.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{}第四站 法国杯站 萨尔德赛车场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.65,0:21:19.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就位前10分钟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.95,0:21:23.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请还在车位上的工作人员马上离开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.25,0:21:27.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请还在车位上的工作人员马上离开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.25,0:21:39.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你真是喜欢赛车场呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.85,0:21:42.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,其实你不必亲自过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.05,0:21:46.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我已经按照指示完成在日本的工作了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.15,0:21:51.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还是说 我来这里会妨碍到你？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.65,0:21:54.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 绝对不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.05,0:21:56.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我非常欢迎呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.85,0:21:57.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还有...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.35,0:21:59.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.05,0:22:02.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爸爸跟我说了一件敏感的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.05,0:22:11.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我要你老实回答
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.45,0:22:14.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你对葵财团的社长宝座有兴趣是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.35,0:22:17.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.85,0:22:19.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.45,0:22:20.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不相信吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.15,0:22:27.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但我很自负我是\N足以创造和葵财团相匹敌的企业的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.85,0:22:30.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不必依赖女人的财产
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.75,0:22:33.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我非常喜欢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.65,0:22:38.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但那并非因为你是葵财团的继承人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.95,0:22:46.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,用不着因为背负着葵财团而摆出那样的防备姿态
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.75,0:22:48.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就算没有葵集团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.25,0:22:50.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你也十分有魅力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.95,0:22:55.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请好好看清我这个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.15,0:22:59.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,直到你能相信我的话是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.95,0:23:03.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第四站 法国锦标赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.95,0:23:07.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,绕过一圈后 又呈现出大家熟悉的情景了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.25,0:23:09.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,从第一位置起跑的弗利兹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.25,0:23:12.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,已经开始和排第二位的加贺拉大差距
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.05,0:23:13.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果胜出这一站
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.05,0:23:14.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就等于开幕后连赢四场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.85,0:23:18.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那就平了2017年风见创下的记录
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.95,0:23:25.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,若是以前的隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.05,0:23:28.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,绝对不会说出那种话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.95,0:23:31.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不是说过无论任何时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.45,0:23:34.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也一定会有机会吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.65,0:23:38.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是 我没有抱着你那种心情参赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.25,0:23:42.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那你们要我怎样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.15,0:24:04.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这个大饭桶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.45,0:24:09.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真不可思议
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.85,0:24:11.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,连起跑时的摇动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.95,0:24:13.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,直线车道的加速没有过失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:14.75,0:24:17.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,无论什么时候都正确冷静地跑在记录在线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.15,0:24:21.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这种事真的可能吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:40.35,0:24:41.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,能回来吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:41.95,0:24:44.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我想没问题 已经进入这边了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:46.85,0:24:48.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:58.35,0:25:00.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,先进入扫瞄室 以后再检查车子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:00.55,0:25:01.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快备份资料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:01.95,0:25:03.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,解除B系统的主程序
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:03.75,0:25:05.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,关上货柜舱口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:32.75,0:25:33.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再注射一支
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:34.15,0:25:36.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是如果大量注射中和剂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:36.75,0:25:37.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别说了!注射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:38.45,0:25:39.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样下去什么都做不成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:40.05,0:25:40.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:41.45,0:25:45.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,弗利兹的退出令比赛变得不明朗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:45.55,0:25:47.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在领先的是布利德‧加贺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:47.95,0:25:50.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是古德利安在他后面
